.field public static final synthetic NO_CORE_LIBRARY_DESUGARING_ERROR_MESSAGE:Ljava/lang/String; = "Error building BillingFlowParams which is required to perform purchases in the Play store. This is due to an issue in Google\'s Billing Client library. Please check https://errors.rev.cat/no-core-library-desugaring for more info and to fix this issue."
